Source: pg-pinyin
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/aiyou178/pg_pinyin

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pinyin
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pinyin
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Pinyin romanization and search helpers for PostgreSQL
  Rust/pgrx extension for pinyin conversion and related query helpers in
  PostgreSQL.
